<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Payment Received - Invoice {{invoice.number}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00A859 0%, #00D26A 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .header p {
            margin: 10px 0 0;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        .success-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 30px 20px;
        }
        .payment-summary {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .amount {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #00A859;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .currency {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .payment-details {
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f3f4;
        }
        .detail-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .detail-row:nth-child(even) {
            background: #fafafa;
        }
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #666;
            min-width: 140px;
            margin-right: 15px;
        }
        .detail-value {
            flex: 1;
            color: #333;
        }
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            background: #e8f5e9;
            color: #2e7d32;
        }
        .zatca-section {
            background: #e3f2fd;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .zatca-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #0078D4;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .qr-placeholder {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            background: white;
            border: 2px dashed #0078D4;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 10px auto;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #0078D4;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .action-buttons {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            margin: 0 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: center;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .btn-primary {
            background: #0078D4;
            color: white;
        }
        .btn-success {
            background: #00A859;
            color: white;
        }
        .next-steps {
            background: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .next-steps-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #856404;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        .footer p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #0078D4;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 0;
                border-radius: 0;
            }
            .detail-row {
                flex-direction: column;
                padding: 15px 20px;
            }
            .detail-label {
                margin-bottom: 5px;
                min-width: auto;
            }
            .btn {
                display: block;
                margin: 10px 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="header">
            <div class="success-icon">âœ…</div>
            <h1>Payment Received</h1>
            <p>Thank you for your payment</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Content -->
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <strong>{{customer.name}}</strong>,</p>
            
            <p>We are pleased to confirm that we have received your payment. Your invoice has been marked as paid.</p>

            <!-- Payment Summary -->
            <div class="payment-summary">
                <div class="amount">
                    {{payment.amount}} <span class="currency">{{payment.currency}}</span>
                </div>
                <p>Payment received on {{formatDate payment.receivedDate}}</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Payment Details -->
            <div class="payment-details">
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">Invoice Number:</div>
                    <div class="detail-value">#{{invoice.number}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">Invoice Date:</div>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{formatDate invoice.date}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">Payment Method:</div>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{payment.method}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">Transaction ID:</div>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{payment.transactionId}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">Payment Status:</div>
                    <div class="detail-value">
                        <span class="status-badge">Paid</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                {{#if payment.reference}}
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">Reference:</div>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{payment.reference}}</div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
            </div>

            {{#if invoice.property}}
            <!-- Property Information -->
            <div class="payment-details">
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">Property:</div>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{invoice.property.name}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">Unit:</div>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{invoice.property.unit}}</div>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">Service Period:</div>
                    <div class="detail-value">{{invoice.servicePeriod}}</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            <!-- ZATCA Compliance Section -->
            {{#if invoice.zatcaCompliant}}
            <div class="zatca-section">
                <div class="zatca-title">ðŸ‡¸ðŸ‡¦ ZATCA E-Invoice</div>
                <p>This payment is for a ZATCA-compliant electronic invoice</p>
                <div class="qr-placeholder">
                    QR Code
                </div>
                <p><small>VAT Registration: {{company.vatNumber}}</small></p>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            <!-- Action Buttons -->
            <div class="action-buttons">
                <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}/invoices/{{invoice.id}}" class="btn btn-primary">
                    View Invoice
                </a>
                <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}/payments/{{payment.id}}/receipt" class="btn btn-success">
                    Download Receipt
                </a>
            </div>

            <!-- Next Steps -->
            {{#if hasOutstandingBalance}}
            <div class="next-steps">
                <div class="next-steps-title">Outstanding Balance</div>
                <p>You still have an outstanding balance of <strong>{{outstandingBalance}} {{payment.currency}}</strong> on your account.</p>
                <p><a href="{{dashboardUrl}}/payments">View all invoices</a> to make additional payments.</p>
            </div>
            {{else}}
            <div class="next-steps">
                <div class="next-steps-title">Account Status</div>
                <p>âœ… Your account is now up to date. Thank you for your prompt payment!</p>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            <p>If you have any questions about this payment or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our accounts team.</p>

            <p>Thank you for choosing Fixzit Enterprise.</p>

            <p>Best regards,<br>
            <strong>Fixzit Enterprise Finance Team</strong></p>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>{{company.name}}</strong></p>
            <p>{{company.address}}</p>
            <p>VAT Number: {{company.vatNumber}} | CR: {{company.crNumber}}</p>
            <p>
                <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}/account">Manage Account</a> | 
                <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}/support">Contact Support</a>
            </p>
            <p>Â© 2025 Fixzit Enterprise. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>